        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="glossary-td"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Subdomain">Subdomain</a></td>
          <td class="glossary-td">A subdomain is a domain that is a part of a main domain.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="glossary-td"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vulnerability_(computing)">Vulnerability</a></td>
          <td class="glossary-td">Avulnerability is a weakness which can be exploited by a Threat Actor.</td>
        </tr>
    </table>
  </div>
